{"tid":1778880,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"可唔可以多一點支持少一點責備","createTime":"2019-12-11T09:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T07:48:51.000Z","uid":343138,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"81fbaf4d9e44bfff5f5cecc69ae8f2ce83cb5e67","tid":1778880,"uid":343138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"我係一個女前缐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（長篇大論，但只係想發洩下&amp;希望香港人團結啲）<br />\n<br />\n活動開始以泥，我有錢出錢，有力出力<br />\n但從來冇公開講乜嘢，因為我覺得我係香港人，我係應份咁做！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但半年過去，真心好攰冇曬動力<br />\n<br />\n係個心好攰<br />\n<br />\n曾經責怪自己點解咁冇用搵咁少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫唔到手足啲乜嘢<br />\n<br />\n到中期愈行愈前做衝衝子<br />\n裝修有人屌，堵路有人屌，連俾人拉都可以有人屌9你柒去送頭<br />\n<br />\n當下都有責怪自己係咪有嘢做得唔啱～反思自己係咪有乜嘢位柒左<br />\n<br />\n有灰心有失望，但都堅持住，一路同自己講！我哋嘅做法唔完美，可以改善！<br />\n<br />\n但到依家！活動已經半年！<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲物資撚因為你幫襯左藍店而屌鳩你，因為一大堆道理而責怪你，但佢哋唔會了解下你之前發生咗咩事<br />\n<br />\n真心灰到想同佢割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係，你地課金買物資，好多謝你地嘅幫忙<br />\n<br />\n但可唔可以唔好當自己係神<br />\n係～你付出金錢，付出時間去送物資<br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過我哋付出左乜嘢？可唔可以屌之前了解下先？<br />\n<br />\n我行左十幾個鐘，攰到仆街乜都末食個！附近得番間翠x！我仲要擔心一陣走唔走到，附近又重狗<br />\n<br />\n我真係好肚餓，諗都冇諗食左翠x！轉頭俾送物資既神知道左，一句＂吓！翠X藍咖喔！你點解仲幫襯？＂<br />\n<br />\n當下好想喊！係！我仆街！唔應該食藍店<br />\n<br />\n我更加唔應該衝咁前搞到自己10幾個鐘冇食飯<br />\n我更加唔應該衝咁前搞到自己中彈毁容<br />\n我最唔應該就係係又餓又痛嘅情況下 <strong>飢不擇食</strong> 咁入咗去食翠華<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔止一次發生類似嘅事，但日積月累之下真係會令人哋情緒崩潰<br />\n<br />\n我唔係要求啲咩加冕，關心<br />\n我只係要求多一點支持少一點責備<br />\n<br />\n呢場活動咁成功係因為大家各自出力，但時間一耐<br />\n大家開始出現互相指責<br />\n有勇武指責和理非，有和理非指責勇武<br />\n<br />\n其實大家要清楚，冇一個人嘅付出係應份，既然係咁，互相遷就互相體諒下唔係更好?<br />\n<br />\n我哋仲未到煲底，可否一齊行落去？"},{"pid":"96efed12c8f0e9b64eb5a94f02ae5c164ad8aca8","tid":1778880,"uid":316537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:36:56.000Z","msg":"撐住"},{"pid":"86790304d6777e3af73c7c0fa28cefd77398c312","tid":1778880,"uid":139671,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:36:58.000Z","msg":"香港人就係中意乜都屌左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655de6d029d38addfb607c0b5b46983c36af5f20","tid":1778880,"uid":122134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:39:06.000Z","msg":"香港人係咁<br />\n憎人富貴厭人貧<br />\n唔係你既錯<br />\n係度代個條廢柴同你講聲<br />\n<br />\n對唔住<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b85b967461584321813e4625234338c25247441","tid":1778880,"uid":12526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:40:50.000Z","msg":"無人想知你係男定女 邊度受左傷阿<br />\nBtw 身同感受"},{"pid":"6773743ad5ca950a3312d6a1c241990a809c9132","tid":1778880,"uid":174639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:45:14.000Z","msg":"辛苦晒手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80c10d016d761e878941b06b6e0356d41d0f3ef","tid":1778880,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T09:52:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[你今日FC咗未] 全港最大的Fact Check平台已經推出了<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776631</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea7d392f241f5268ac46fecfa544bc03ec5eeb10","tid":1778880,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過屌你果D好大機會係左膠/ 五毛<br />\n唔係同路人黎<br />\n唔洗擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n辛苦手足"},{"pid":"a9944f18efbb29f2a5b546a9defc432095d09a1f","tid":1778880,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"連儂牆嘅重要性 大家係唔係真係知道？對家就嚟贏啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1784660\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1784660</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n唔好意思借一借位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家推翻啲行動post 好冇 唔好將呢度淪為香討<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arcdYNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarcdYNL.jpg&h=0c66eabf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tf9LPUr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftf9LPUr.jpg&h=321d1e24&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1c884525a5bdb60c032f0f1f2e76e6f227d0a40","tid":1778880,"uid":77164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:25:28.000Z","msg":"你地做左太多野，我地無資格講割唔割"},{"pid":"185fb476820410a0f8dab228d2d169b7b54ac7fb","tid":1778880,"uid":256514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:26:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6a6469bb9f49ae92a85714424a94baac5fe2c6e","tid":1778880,"uid":185656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:27:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c129d869c551c0e7ab0287c30942b5f6fd9e4b","tid":1778880,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e0409f2733105f5e3974be454e7c981d86089bc","tid":1778880,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:29:34.000Z","msg":"加油<br />\n<br />\n之前有人捐大家樂同老麥飯卷都畀人屌<br />\n<br />\n其實唔係咁多黃店又方便又有飯卷買"},{"pid":"3c49dbf213fca8b71619e8598eb7676f9b3bc2a1","tid":1778880,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"試下解釋下自己<br />\n雖然係自己人都代表人地識讀心嘛<br />\n同路人:翠華藍架喎<br />\n你答咁我忙左十幾個鐘,又搵唔到野食<br />\n得返翠華未豪比佢囉,我都要食野架<br />\n<br />\n佢未必理解到,但都未必會屌你呢"},{"pid":"d7137cdd4d1ace4104082dce8e60292c71f1c62d","tid":1778880,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T07:48:51.000Z","msg":"我覺得 做到咪盡做 做唔到可以有走棧位<br />\n總之達到目的 不需要過多的政治潔癖"}]}